    A1200   OS 3.0   68020 14Mhz                2Mb of Chip
    A1200   OS 3.0   68020 28Mhz                2Mb of Chip +   4Mb of Fast
    A1200   OS 3.0   68030 50Mhz + 68882 50Mhz  2Mb of Chip +   4Mb of Fast



